name: 90's Sweets Freakshake
description:
Every sweetness is stacked in the freakshake style dessert. From the fresh “es doger” for the base, into fluffy “kue apem beras” on the top. It contains the legendary stretch candy, “arbanat”, gem rose biscuit, and many more to bring back your sweet childhood. 
We only served a dozen of them, so grab them fast!
